hopobject.body: A Second Class stamp kifaru 500 light back pouch Vice President Binay had acted alone without the blessing of the President in forging a ceasefire agreement with the rebel Misuari which resulted to a humiliating failure. This is a ploy for political mileage as he is aiming for the 2016 presidency which backfired straight on his face a day after talking to the media of his accomplishment. Poor Binay who is very desperate to become a President against a strong contender Mar Roxas who is not tainted with any corruption groomed and supported by President Aquino.
